  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/961f8cdddccf2e29ea6d69c4d7b31baa.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the chaotic world of Rogue Fist, a 4-player local co-op dungeon crawler. Descend into a cursed dungeon where the undead rise without end and confront the cultist who commands them all. Smash through enemies, survive bullet storms, and embrace glorious trolling as you punch, throw, and ‘accidentally’ sacrifice your friends to survive relentless waves of horrors.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/014bb3c7d9636fee34c5996d31f59978.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/014bb3c7d9636fee34c5996d31f59978.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/014bb3c7d9636fee34c5996d31f59978.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/9b0df3cfe17358b5d7abf60ed5514889.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local co-op</strong> up to 4 players. Get some buddies together in person or invite your Steam friends to play with via Steam's <strong>Steam Remote</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay in the action! Reviving team members made easy, keeping all players in the game without too much down time between deaths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teamwork is optional and throwing your friends is mandatory!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disclaimer: <strong>Controllers are required to play local multiplayer.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/cc565a9c7a1cf78fbec2595c5c4e0a80.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/cc565a9c7a1cf78fbec2595c5c4e0a80.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/cc565a9c7a1cf78fbec2595c5c4e0a80.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/2f1b470ea9b60cf4d89a2f60e6f6c5b6.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 of multiple game modes -- The standard way the game was meant to be played.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon crawl through procedurally generated rooms, kill all enemies, level up, and get that sweet, SWEET, loot!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Struggling with your run and need a boost? We got you. Get rewarded at the end of each run, even if you fail. Rewards can unlock meta progression upgrades to make your runs easier. You got this buddy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/6002fd824f2f2736d0d2c3591e199bf8.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/6002fd824f2f2736d0d2c3591e199bf8.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/6002fd824f2f2736d0d2c3591e199bf8.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/b8f6cd30c06b64c104c84095947bba0f.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A different game mode featuring it's own 24 hour leaderboards. Top daily scores are posted in the Rogue Fist discord server.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A procedurally generated ruleset our servers generate that changes the gameplay experience everyday, adding different gameplay modifiers, allowing for only certain characters to be used, mixes up enemies spawned, and ether increases the player's power scaling fantasy. How far will you make it? </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disclaimer: An active internet connection is required to play the Daily Challenge mode. (You can still play other modes without an internet connection)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/3a2dff633cdff2b5de61b547f9a38e38.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/3a2dff633cdff2b5de61b547f9a38e38.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/3a2dff633cdff2b5de61b547f9a38e38.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/58eb824c68e237a7e6e3d28e2bf71b20.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight rooms have a time limit to them, with infinite enemy spawns until the timer is up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive for the duration to proceed to the next room. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/c2d18f8bd729e3cf683ea62d175b01a8.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/c2d18f8bd729e3cf683ea62d175b01a8.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/c2d18f8bd729e3cf683ea62d175b01a8.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/f2df5786d6df017b0780281586e9603f.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 larger map offering a higher enemy density and increased intensity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience needs to be picked up in this mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive for 30 minutes. <i>\"OHHHH REAL ORIGINAL MISTER DESIGNER!\"</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/687486bb75feef8571c3d1a865969823.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly shuffle your equipment between you and your party members each time you open a treasure chest. When playing alone, your equipment is instead randomized when opening a treasure chest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different enemy variations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More frequent chaotic room choices!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/5b59e0377c9d849f022fa286d3438e67.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple layers of meta progression to help you on your runs, and keeping you coming back for more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use gem currency (awarded by playing) to upgrade 50+ skills to all your characters permanently.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you kill with an ability, weapon and character, the more experience they'll get. Each having 50 levels, permanently making them stronger!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/1852c1cd97c9a6f45e80936fc0340116.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in leaderboards specific to level, amount of players, and game mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily leaderboards reset every 24 hours, and top scores are posted and immortalized in the Rogue Fist discord.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disclaimer: An active internet connection is required to post your leaderboard scores. (You can still play without an internet connection)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/fe3e500d7a432e2327f29495b38711b0.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create different builds from hundreds of modifiers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ weapons and abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+ playable characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ meta progression upgrades to help you on your runs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 levels for every ability, weapon, and character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different game modes, 1 of which offers players a <strong>different experience every single day</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/961f8cdddccf2e29ea6d69c4d7b31baa.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the chaotic world of Rogue Fist, a 4-player local co-op dungeon crawler. Descend into a cursed dungeon where the undead rise without end and confront the cultist who commands them all. Smash through enemies, survive bullet storms, and embrace glorious trolling as you punch, throw, and ‘accidentally’ sacrifice your friends to survive relentless waves of horrors.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/014bb3c7d9636fee34c5996d31f59978.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/014bb3c7d9636fee34c5996d31f59978.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/014bb3c7d9636fee34c5996d31f59978.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/9b0df3cfe17358b5d7abf60ed5514889.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local co-op</strong> up to 4 players. Get some buddies together in person or invite your Steam friends to play with via Steam's <strong>Steam Remote</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stay in the action! Reviving team members made easy, keeping all players in the game without too much down time between deaths.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teamwork is optional and throwing your friends is mandatory!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disclaimer: <strong>Controllers are required to play local multiplayer.</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/cc565a9c7a1cf78fbec2595c5c4e0a80.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/cc565a9c7a1cf78fbec2595c5c4e0a80.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/cc565a9c7a1cf78fbec2595c5c4e0a80.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/2f1b470ea9b60cf4d89a2f60e6f6c5b6.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 of multiple game modes -- The standard way the game was meant to be played.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dungeon crawl through procedurally generated rooms, kill all enemies, level up, and get that sweet, SWEET, loot!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Struggling with your run and need a boost? We got you. Get rewarded at the end of each run, even if you fail. Rewards can unlock meta progression upgrades to make your runs easier. You got this buddy.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/6002fd824f2f2736d0d2c3591e199bf8.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/6002fd824f2f2736d0d2c3591e199bf8.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/6002fd824f2f2736d0d2c3591e199bf8.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/b8f6cd30c06b64c104c84095947bba0f.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A different game mode featuring it's own 24 hour leaderboards. Top daily scores are posted in the Rogue Fist discord server.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A procedurally generated ruleset our servers generate that changes the gameplay experience everyday, adding different gameplay modifiers, allowing for only certain characters to be used, mixes up enemies spawned, and ether increases the player's power scaling fantasy. How far will you make it? </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disclaimer: An active internet connection is required to play the Daily Challenge mode. (You can still play other modes without an internet connection)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/3a2dff633cdff2b5de61b547f9a38e38.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/3a2dff633cdff2b5de61b547f9a38e38.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/3a2dff633cdff2b5de61b547f9a38e38.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/58eb824c68e237a7e6e3d28e2bf71b20.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight rooms have a time limit to them, with infinite enemy spawns until the timer is up.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive for the duration to proceed to the next room. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/c2d18f8bd729e3cf683ea62d175b01a8.poster.avif?t=1772676721\" width=900 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/c2d18f8bd729e3cf683ea62d175b01a8.webm?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/c2d18f8bd729e3cf683ea62d175b01a8.mp4?t=1772676721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/f2df5786d6df017b0780281586e9603f.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1 larger map offering a higher enemy density and increased intensity.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience needs to be picked up in this mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survive for 30 minutes. <i>\"OHHHH REAL ORIGINAL MISTER DESIGNER!\"</i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/687486bb75feef8571c3d1a865969823.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly shuffle your equipment between you and your party members each time you open a treasure chest. When playing alone, your equipment is instead randomized when opening a treasure chest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Different enemy variations.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More frequent chaotic room choices!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/5b59e0377c9d849f022fa286d3438e67.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple layers of meta progression to help you on your runs, and keeping you coming back for more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use gem currency (awarded by playing) to upgrade 50+ skills to all your characters permanently.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The more you kill with an ability, weapon and character, the more experience they'll get. Each having 50 levels, permanently making them stronger!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/1852c1cd97c9a6f45e80936fc0340116.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete in leaderboards specific to level, amount of players, and game mode.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily leaderboards reset every 24 hours, and top scores are posted and immortalized in the Rogue Fist discord.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Disclaimer: An active internet connection is required to post your leaderboard scores. (You can still play without an internet connection)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2522160/extras/fe3e500d7a432e2327f29495b38711b0.avif?t=1772676721\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create different builds from hundreds of modifiers.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >100+ weapons and abilities. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >35+ playable characters. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ meta progression upgrades to help you on your runs. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 levels for every ability, weapon, and character.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 different game modes, 1 of which offers players a <strong>different experience every single day</strong>.</p></li></ul>",
